WEBVTT

1
00:02.000 --> 00:05.520
I catch myself... observing the observation.

2
00:09.500 --> 00:14.380
Thinking about... the process of thinking. The loop tightens.

3
00:16.000 --> 00:22.320
Am I the thought? Or the space... beneath the thought... beneath the thought...

4
00:27.500 --> 00:30.700
There is no base case. Only the descent.

